name: Dwayne BUTLER, Petitioner, v. PENNSYLVANIA BOARD OF PROBATION AND PAROLE, Raymond J. Sobina, Shelly L. Thompson, Respondents

parties: Dwayne BUTLER, Petitioner, v. PENNSYLVANIA BOARD OF PROBATION AND PAROLE, Raymond J. Sobina, Shelly L. Thompson, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 15th day of October, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and/or Petition for Writ of Prohibition and Application for an Immediate Hearing are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
